## After: Accessible Contrast

<Preview>
  <div class="p-6 bg-white font-sans max-w-sm border border-gray-100 rounded-xl shadow-sm space-y-3">
    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">Welcome back</h3>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">Here's what's happening in your account today. Everything looks great — no issues to report.</p>
    <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
      <button class="bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white text-sm px-4 py-2.5 rounded-md font-medium transition-colors">Get started</button>
      <span class="text-sm text-gray-500">or <span class="text-blue-600 cursor-pointer font-medium">sign in</span></span>
    </div>
  </div>
